OL,5, Rishi Sunak is under pressure from     
OL,6, ministers to increase housing benefit  
OL,7, amid record numbers of people in       
OL,8, temporary housing, the BBC has learned.
OL,10,FHousing Secretary Michael Gove and Work
OL,11,Fand Pensions Secretary Mel Stride have 
OL,12,Fwritten to the prime minister and the  
OL,13,Fchancellor demanding an increase in    
OL,14,FLocal Housing Allowance rates.         
OL,16,FBut the Treasury instead prefers higher
OL,17,Funiversal credit for those in work.    
OL,19,FA final announcement is likely in the  
OL,20,FAutumn Statement later in November.    
